sentences.sentence: In March 2013, the federal court of Australia made orders to appoint Robert Graham Killer of Grant Thornton and Michael Gerrard McCann as the joint provisional liquidators to MOGS Ltd.
sentences.translation: 2013年3月，澳大利亚联邦法院命令，任命罗伯特·格雷厄姆和迈克尔·杰拉德麦肯作为MOGS有限公司联合临时清盘人。
